   </teiHeader> <facsimile> <graphic url="1899_AS_RBH_3_00011.jpeg"/> <graphic url="1899_AS_RBH_3_00012.jpeg"/> </facsimile> <text type="card"> <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1899_AS_RBH_3_00012.jpeg"/><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb946" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Vahrn</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine>bei <hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb43040" type="place">Brixen</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb423" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Tirol</hi></rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1899_AS_RBH_3_00011.jpeg"/>24. 9. 99.</dateline></opener><p>Will hier 8 Tage bleiben, arbeiten</p><p>Bitte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreiben Sie mir, auch <rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Hugo</rs>, wie’s Ihnen geht, und was die Arbeit macht. Ich wohne <rs ref="#pmb43055" type="place">Parkhotel</rs>.</p><p>Die Ovation hab ich erhalten. <rs ref="#pmb11485" type="person">Paul</rs> ist heut nach <rs ref="#pmb263" type="place">Florenz</rs>.</p></div></body> </text></TEI>